    "Manual searches of major software engineering venues and backward snowballing added 27 and 11 new papers, respectively, yielding a combined pool of 353 candidate papers.",
    "Subsequently, all papers in this pool underwent a multi-stage screening process.",
    "First, we conducted a manual screening based on our pre-defined inclusion criteria to exclude literature irrelevant to the core topic.",
    "To ensure methodological rigor, the exclusion of any paper required unanimous agreement among all participating researchers.",
